Backend Restart for Code Reload Log
===================================
Test Time: 2025-06-17 14:47
Purpose: Document backend restart to reload Python code changes

Issue:
- "Failed to load chat sessions" error when opening project
- Backend logs showed it was still using old code (ProjectResponse instead of ProjectInfo)

Root Cause:
- Python code changes require backend restart to take effect
- Even though we're mounting the source directory, Python imports are cached
- The previous validation error fix wasn't applied until restart

Action Taken:
- Restarted backend container with: docker restart deer-flow-backend
- Backend successfully reloaded with the fixed code

Current Status:
- Backend running successfully
- Code changes are now active
- Project session loading should work properly

Note: For future Python code changes in the backend, always restart the container to ensure changes take effect.